No. 10-5467. Jorge Olivera, Petitioner v. United States. 562 U.S. 954, 131 S. Ct. 304,

178 L. Ed. 2d 253,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 7839. October 4, 2010.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.
